manifests.contents:
bench = []
example = []
test = []

[[bin]]
bench = true
doc = true
doctest = true
edition = "2018"
harness = true
name = "genshin-gacha-exporter"
path = "src/main.rs"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
required-features = []
test = true

[dependencies]
anyhow = "1.0.38"
chrono = "0.4.19"
console = "0.14.0"
dialoguer = "0.7.1"
enum-map = "0.6.4"
futures = "0.3.12"
hyper-rustls = "0.22.1"
indicatif = "0.15.0"
lazy_static = "1.4.0"
rustls = "0.19.0"
serde_with = "1.6.2"
tokio-rustls = "0.22.0"

[dependencies.hyper]
features = ["server", "client", "http1", "http2", "tcp"]
optional = false
version = "0.14.2"

[dependencies.rcgen]
features = ["x509-parser"]
optional = false
version = "0.8.9"

[dependencies.reqwest]
features = ["json", "gzip", "cookies"]
optional = false
version = "0.11.0"

[dependencies.serde]
features = ["derive"]
optional = false
version = "1.0.123"

[dependencies.tokio]
features = ["rt-multi-thread", "macros", "net", "io-util"]
optional = false
version = "1.1.1"

[package]
authors = ["Youmu <johnmave126@gmail.com>"]
autobenches = true
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
categories = []
edition = "2018"
keywords = []
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
name = "genshin-gacha-exporter"
publish = true
version = "0.2.5"
[target."cfg(windows)".build-dependencies]

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies]
proxyconf = "0.2.1"
win32console = "0.1.4"

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies.ctrlc]
features = ["termination"]
optional = false
version = "3.1.7"

[target."cfg(windows)".dev-dependencies]
